 fibre d’acacia","heading_size":"h4","html_tag":"p","indent":"none","highlight_effect":"default","highlight_accent_color":"","highlight_text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"rich_text_jePeKT":{"type":"rich-text","settings":{"text":"<p>Prébiotique doux issu de la sève d'acacia, il nourrit tes bonnes bactéries intestinales. Résultat concret : ton ventre gonfle moins, ta digestion devient plus légère. Un microbiote équilibré, c'est aussi moins de fringales émotionnelles.<\/p>","content_width":"sm"},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["button_3qwGJE","image_MWK6YF","heading_4zdcHj","rich_text_jePeKT"]},"multi_column_column_yFpJHg":{"type":"_multi-column-column","name":"t:sections.multi_column.blocks.column.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","text_alignment":"left"},"blocks":{"button_GwFadL":{"type":"button","name":"t:blocks.button.name","settings":{"text":"Essayer Uburn — 30 kcal →","url":"\/products\/ube-poudre","open_in_new_tab":false,"style":"solid","background":"","text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"image_V6JC4H":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ingredient_Coco.jpg","max_width":100,"mobile_max_width":100},"blocks":{}},"heading_pjabzM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"MCT de coco","heading_size":"h4","html_tag":"p","indent":"none","highlight_effect":"default","highlight_accent_color":"","highlight_text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"rich_text_qyTtfz":{"type":"rich-text","settings":{"text":"<p>Les MCT du coco fournissent une énergie rapide et propre, directement utilisable par ton corps. Résultat concret : plus de coup de barre à 15h, plus besoin de café pour tenir. Tu restes alerte et concentrée — sans pic glycémique ni crash énergétique.<\/p>","content_width":"sm"},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["button_GwFadL","image_V6JC4H","heading_pjabzM","rich_text_qyTtfz"]},"multi_column_column_f3HxVd":{"type":"_multi-column-column","name":"t:sections.multi_column.blocks.column.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","text_alignment":"left"},"blocks":{"button_gQPQCP":{"type":"button","name":"t:blocks.button.name","settings":{"text":"Essayer Uburn — 30 kcal →","url":"\/products\/ube-poudre","open_in_new_tab":false,"style":"solid","background":"","text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"image_tGiEJc":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ingredient_Gingembre.jpg","max_width":100,"mobile_max_width":100},"blocks":{}},"heading_nkEUCm":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"Le gingembre violet","heading_size":"h4","html_tag":"p","indent":"none","highlight_effect":"default","highlight_accent_color":"","highlight_text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"rich_text_TKLVcV":{"type":"rich-text","settings":{"text":"<p>Le gingembre violet active ton métabolisme de l'intérieur. Résultat concret : ton corps brûle plus de calories au repos, ta digestion devient fluide dès les premiers jours. Tu sens une chaleur douce qui signale que ça travaille vraiment.<\/p>","content_width":"sm"},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["button_gQPQCP","image_tGiEJc","heading_nkEUCm","rich_text_TKLVcV"]},"multi_column_column_XVg6H9":{"type":"_multi-column-column","name":"t:sections.multi_column.blocks.column.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","text_alignment":"left"},"blocks":{"button_ePn6kH":{"type":"button","name":"t:blocks.button.name","settings":{"text":"Essayer Uburn — 30 kcal →","url":"\/products\/ube-poudre","open_in_new_tab":false,"style":"solid","background":"","text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"image_DDdddL":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ingredient_L-carnitine_tartrate.jpg","max_width":100,"mobile_max_width":100},"blocks":{}},"heading_gne9Pj":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"L-carnitine tartrate","heading_size":"h4","html_tag":"p","indent":"none","highlight_effect":"default","highlight_accent_color":"","highlight_text_color":""},"blocks":{}},"rich_text_UYPtfp":{"type":"rich-text","settings":{"text":"<p>La L-carnitine tartrate transporte les graisses stockées directement vers tes cellules musculaires pour les brûler. Résultat concre